<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow" data-aos="fade-up"><%- include('../partials/icon', { name: 'building-2', cls: 'inline-icon' }) %> Our Story</p>
    <h1 data-aos="fade-up">From Corporate Kitchens to Your Everyday Table</h1>
    <p class="lead" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
      Thali & More began in a working kitchen in Mahishbathan, cooking fresh, hygienic meals at scale for corporate offices across Sector V. Today, that same kitchen, the same standards, and the same discipline deliver healthy home-style meals straight to homes, PGs and offices across New Town, Sector V, Salt Lake and Rajarhat.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container grid grid--2 grid--align-center">
    <div data-aos="fade-right">
      <p class="eyebrow">Where It Started</p>
      <h2>A Kitchen Built for Consistency, Not Convenience</h2>
      <p>Long before we delivered to individual homes, our Mahishbathan kitchen was already feeding hundreds of employees every day through corporate catering contracts across Sector V's IT parks. That meant one thing above all: food had to be consistent, on time, and safe, every single day, without exception.</p>
      <p>That operational backbone is what makes Thali &amp; More different from a typical home-tiffin service. We're not scaling up from someone's home kitchen. We're scaling down from an enterprise-grade kitchen to serve you personally.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-visual" data-aos="fade-left">
      <div class="stat-grid">
        <div class="stat-card stat-card--light">
          <span class="stat-card__value"><%- include('../partials/icon', { name: 'building-2', cls: 'icon-lg' }) %></span>
          <span class="stat-card__label">Corporate Catering Since Day One</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card stat-card--light">
          <span class="stat-card__value" data-counter="<%= site.stats.subscribers %>">0</span>
          <span class="stat-card__label">Subscribers Today</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card stat-card--light">
          <span class="stat-card__value" data-counter="<%= site.stats.mealsDelivered %>">0</span>
          <span class="stat-card__label">Meals Delivered</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card stat-card--light">
          <span class="stat-card__value"><%- include('../partials/icon', { name: 'map-pin', cls: 'icon-lg' }) %></span>
          <span class="stat-card__label">4 Localities Served</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--tint">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section__head" data-aos="fade-up">
      <p class="eyebrow">Our Mission</p>
      <h2>Why We Exist</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid--3">
      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up">
        <div class="feature-card__icon"><%- include('../partials/icon', { name: 'heart' }) %></div>
        <h3>Home Should Taste Like Home</h3>
        <p>Working professionals shouldn't have to choose between eating healthy and eating well. We cook the way a family kitchen would, just at scale.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
        <div class="feature-card__icon"><%- include('../partials/icon', { name: 'shield-check' }) %></div>
        <h3>Trust Is Earned Daily</h3>
        <p>Every delivery is a promise kept: on time, hygienic, and exactly what you subscribed for. No surprises, no shortcuts.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
        <div class="feature-card__icon"><%- include('../partials/icon', { name: 'sparkles' }) %></div>
        <h3>Convenience Without Compromise</h3>
        <p>Subscribing should feel effortless. Pausing, changing plans or asking questions should never feel like a fight.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container final-cta__box glass-card" data-aos="zoom-in">
    <h2>Taste the Difference Corporate-Grade Consistency Makes</h2>
    <p>Start with a 7-day trial and see why offices across Sector V already trust our kitchen.</p>
    <div class="hero__ctas">
      <a href="/#trial" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Start 7-Day Trial</a>
      <a href="/plans" class="btn btn--outline btn--lg">View Plans</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
